<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
        <meta name="description" content="" />
        <meta name="author" content="" />
        <title>원격 진료 시스템</title>
        <!-- Favicon-->
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="assets/favicon.ico" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" type="text/css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" type="text/css">
        <!-- jquery -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <!-- Responsive navbar-->
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="">원격 진료 시스템</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation"><span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span></button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="javascript:openModal('login-patient');">환자 로그인</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="javascript:openModal('login-doctor');">의사 로그인</a></li>
                        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="">서비스 소개</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="title">
            <h2>원격 진료 시스템</h2>
            <p>
                원격 진료 시스템은 일상 생활에 지장을 주지 않으면서 치료 접근성을 향상시킬 수 있고,
                빠른 시간내에 환자의 건강 모니터링 정보를 받고 분석할 수 있는 의료 시스템입니다.
            </p>
            <div class="loginBtn">
                <button onclick="javascript:openModal('login-patient')");">환자 로그인</button>
                <button onclick="javascript:openModal('login-doctor')">의사 로그인</button>
            </div>
            
        </div>

        <!-- Patient Login -->
        <div id="modal"></div>
        <div class="modal-con login-patient">
            <div class="con">
                <p>환자 로그인</p>
                <form class="login" action='/login?identity=patient' method='POST'>
                    <input type="input" name="inputCode" placeholder="환자 코드를 입력하세요.">
                    <input type="submit" value="로그인">
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Doctor Login -->
        <div id="modal"></div>
        <div class="modal-con login-doctor">
            <div class="con">
                <p>의사 로그인</p>
                <form class="login" action='/login?identity=doctor' method='POST'>
                    <input type="text" name="inputCode" placeholder="의사 코드를 입력하세요.">
                    <input type="submit" value="로그인">
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script>
            function openModal(modalname){
                document.get
                $("#modal").fadeIn(300);
                $("."+modalname).fadeIn(300);
            }

            $("#modal, .close").on('click',function(){
                $("#modal").fadeOut(300);
                $(".modal-con").fadeOut(300);
            });
        </script>

        <!-- Bootstrap core JS-->
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
